---
title: "supportsInterface (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check: check interfaceId
    q_check --> q_true: super.supportsInterface(interfaceId) == true
    q_true --> [*]: return true
    q_check --> q_check_receiver: super.supportsInterface(interfaceId) == false
    q_check_receiver --> q_true2: interfaceId == type(IReceiver).interfaceId
    q_true2 --> [*]: return true
    q_check_receiver --> q_false: interfaceId != type(IReceiver).interfaceId
    q_false --> [*]: return false

    note right of q_check
        INV-001: supports both PausableWithAccessControl interfaces and IReceiver
        INV-002: override resolution: PausableWithAccessControl then IERC165
    end note
